:'''Antonia:''' Let's see... oh, yes, there is indeed something that could use your help.
:'''Antonia:''' An elderly mine cart operator intends to retire, but... he's not really hitting it off with his current apprentice. I guess you already know what I'm getting at. If the apprentice can't complete his training, then the master won't be able to retire in peace.
:'''Antonia:''' So, I'd like to ask you to be... um... assistant instructor for that not-so-bright apprentice.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Assistant instructor?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_701060109-->
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Uh, no. I know nothing of mining carts.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_701060109-->
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} I know just the man for this job. His name is Sampo...
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_701060108-->
::'''Antonia:''' Huh? No way. He'd bring nothing but trouble.
:'''Antonia:''' Relax. Though the title is "assistant instructor," it doesn't actually require much technical know-how.
:'''Antonia:''' That senior mine cart operator is very capable, but he has a bad temper and can be very stubborn. Things would be good if he had a gifted apprentice to begin with, but that's sadly not the case right now... So please find a way to help him.
:'''Antonia:''' What say you? Can you do me this favor?
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Not a problem. Leave it to me.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} I suppose I can give it a try...
:<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_701060114-->
:'''Antonia:''' They usually stay at the vagrant shelter in the mines. I've already told that senior mine cart operator about this. When you see him, just say my name, and he'll know.
:<!--Ends the current performance-->
:<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_5010277_24-->
:<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_5010277_24-->
:{{DIcon|Talk}} I heard that the mine hasn't been peaceful lately.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501027715-->
::'''Antonia:''' Yes. As you saw last time in the mine, it's been a bit chaotic... but it will end. The vagrants will stop messing around sooner or later.
::'''Antonia:''' After all, they've got mouths to feed. If they really got rid of all the professional mining teams, those hooligans won't be able to make a living.
::'''Antonia:''' They are well aware of this, which is why they have never crossed the line. A small reward goes a long way with them. I just didn't expect the news to get all the way to Svarog this time...
:;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:{{DIcon|Talk}} I heard you recruited some of the vagrants into the mining team.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501027719-->
::'''Antonia:''' Well, how should I put it...? Life isn't easy. If Boulder Town also gets eroded by the Fragmentum, we will have to find another livelihood. Who wouldn't want some help at a time like that?
::'''Antonia:''' But the old miners have their own ideas. They think the vagrants have made a mess of the mining team... and the vagrants aren't happy with their payment and feel that they've lost freedom... In the end, neither side is happy.
::'''Antonia:''' But I know what I am doing. This minor setback will not change my mind. Don't worry about it.
:;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:{{DIcon|Talk}} Do you have any recommendations for activities in the underground?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501027723-->
::'''Antonia:''' The Fight Club is quite popular. But personally, I wouldn't pay a shield for that kind of cheap show. It's vulgar and low-class.
::'''Antonia:''' There is a restaurant, the one owned by Gertie. The food there is quite good... so long as Gertie doesn't come up with some weird recipes on a whim...
::'''Antonia:''' Also, I heard there will be a rap concert where the vagrants are? I don't know how to appreciate that kind of thing, so I've never been there. Go check it out if you are interested. Just be careful there.
:;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:{{DIcon|Exit}} That's all questions I have.
::<!--Custom String Listener: ALL_TALK_END-->
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
