;(If {{cx}}<!--SubMission Finish: 101150231--> and {{cx}}<!--SubMission Started: 201040101-->)
:{{DIcon}} How have things been?
::'''Antonia:''' Well, rumor has it that the Overworld and Underworld are opening up to each other again, so I've been busy with that.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Busy doing what?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501027733-->
:::'''Antonia:''' It's just a business thing. I'm still ironing out the details with some Overworld entrepreneurs &mdash; even if we're still only at the letter-writing stage.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} What do you think about the lifting of the blockade?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501027735-->
:::'''Antonia:''' You asking me? I reckon the good outweighs the bad.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_501027736-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501027736-->
::'''Antonia:''' During the days of the blockade, I could only rely on my mining for work &mdash; and despite leaving me with enough money and my miners' wages, this Underworld and its economy are stagnant. There's no trickling down of funds or goods...
::'''Antonia:''' But now the blockade's lifted &mdash; well, things are completely different. I can invest my assets into anything I want, and I'll wait for that compound interest to start snowballing &mdash; that's how you make money, see.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Who do you invest in?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501027739-->
::'''Antonia:''' Let me think... There's a private manufacturer that makes Geomarrow gear, and another military one that produces robots.
::'''Antonia:''' Oh yeah, that's right &mdash; I also got in touch with a real estate agent called Lavonne. Her project looks promising... if what she's saying is actually true.
::'''Antonia:''' In short... I'll have to wait and see.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Any other changes around here besides those?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501027743-->
::'''Antonia:''' Are you an investigative reporter, or is this commercial espionage!? All these detailed questions... But I know I can trust you &mdash; after all, you're the generous soul one who saved our mine.
::'''Antonia:''' If you ask me, the other biggest change has got to be &mdash; that I've finally got somewhere to spend my money. I've always dreamed of going to the Golden Theater up in the Overworld...
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
;(If {{cx}}<!--SubMission Started: 404011701-->, {{cx}}<!--SubMission Finish: 101150231-->, and {{cx}}<!--SubMission Started: 201040101-->)
:{{DIcon|?}} I'm looking for some EXTRA DOUGH. You know what I mean?
::'''Antonia:''' (Trailblazer), you mean...
::'''Antonia:''' Heh. You must be pretty desperate if you are coming to me for work.
::'''Antonia:''' I'm not judging. The mining team can never be too big. Anyway, you have tools to work with?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I have two iron hands!
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404011706-->
:::'''Antonia:''' The way you say that... you're being serious?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} How about this baseball bat?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404011708-->
:::'''Antonia:''' Hmm. I've seen this thing of yours in action. It definitely is solid, but shouldn't you hold on to it to fight?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} No.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404011710-->
:::'''Antonia:''' Heh. Aren't you just an honest soul? If you're gonna beg, you better bring a bowl.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_404011711-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404011711-->
::'''Antonia:''' Normally, I don't lend mining tools without a cash deposit or something to serve as collateral... This isn't me being stingy here. It's just the environment. There are way too many people out there who go back on their word and try to nickle and dime me.
::'''Antonia:''' That said. I do trust you. Hmm. I just so happen to have a mostly new, second-hand pickax. Take it.
::'''Antonia:''' You still remember that massive Geomarrow in the Great Mine? I suggest you head out that way first and try your luck. Oh, right. If you dig up anything interesting, don't forget to bring it to me for an appraisal.
::'''Antonia:''' Good luck, (Trailblazer) the rookie miner.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Talk_404011701-->
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
;(If {{cx}}<!--SubMission Started: 404011705-->, {{cx}}<!--SubMission Started: 404011701-->, {{cx}}<!--SubMission Finish: 101150231-->, and {{cx}}<!--SubMission Started: 201040101-->)
:{{DIcon|?}} Umm... So about making some extra dough...
::'''Antonia:''' Oh. That. Yeah, I remember. What about it, (Trailblazer)? Everything going well with your mining gig?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Something kind of unexpected happened...
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404011764-->
:::'''Antonia:''' ...Unexpected?
:::'''Antonia:''' Oh... I think I understand. Let me guess, you broke the pickax, right?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I broke the pickax you lent me.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404011767-->
:::'''Antonia:''' ...Huh? You've barely been at it for half a day &mdash;
:::'''Antonia:''' Ahem. Anyway. I suppose I'm partly to blame. I did give professional equipment to an absolute noobie.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_404011769-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404011769-->
::'''Antonia:''' Let me guess... Someone isn't going to take no for an answer and wants me to lend them equipment again. Is that right?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} You are right on the money.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} They say the third time's the charm.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404011772-->
::'''Antonia:''' ...I get it. I'll trust you one more time. I have one more pickax lying around. Take it.
::'''Antonia:''' But, ahem, I will be taking a deposit... I hope you can understand.
::'''Antonia:''' How about just 500 credits?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I won't disappoint you.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404011776-->
